data.description: Welcome to Carolina Park; One of Mount Pleasant's most sought after neighborhoods! This beautiful, family friendly home has FIVE bedrooms, a large primary suite downstairs, and a huge bonus room upstairs that would make the perfect media or play room. You will love the open concept on the first floor. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a butler's pantry that connects to the formal dining room with extra counter space for additional storage. Upstairs you will find fresh, new carpet throughout! There is an office/ bedroom with french doors that is absolutely charming with access to a private veranda. This home has a detached garage, screened in porch, patio, fire-pit, fenced-in-yard and more.This home is conveniently located close to the neighborhood amenities that include pool, tennis/ pickleball courts and dog park. Jump on your golf cart and take the kids to school at Carolina Park Elementary or Wando High. There is so much to love about this home and neighborhood. Schedule your showing today!
